column1: From 2:30 a.m. to 5:30 a.m. on 7/25/2023, Lawson reports that there's "no data from weather channel," and leaves the all fields except person blank
Starting on 7/25/2023, many fields are left blank, especially when "Lawson" is the person recording
"LiLes" spells their name with an uppercase "L" in the middle.
At 6:30 p.m. on 7/25/2023, Lawson signs as the person recording, even though the handwriting used in the other fields matches the handwriting of "LiLes"
The date is corrected from "7-20-2023" to "7-30-2023" for page for "7-30-2023"
Usual gap of NA hi_wc values in the mornings of each day.
